.TH LIBBSM 3LIB "Mar 6, 2017"
.SH NAME
libbsm \- basic security library
.SH SYNOPSIS
.LP
.nf
cc [ \fIflag\fR... ] \fIfile\fR. \fB-lbsm\fR [ \fIlibrary\fR... ]
.fi

.SH DESCRIPTION
.LP
Functions in this library provide basic security, library object reuse, and
auditing.
.SH INTERFACES
.LP
